Description: SFCGAL bindings for PHP — ISO 19107 / OGC SFA 1.2 3D
 SFCGAL is a C++ wrapper library around CGAL that supports
 ISO 19107:2013 and OGC Simple Features Access 1.2 for 3D operations.
 It exposes a stable C API used by PostGIS, QGIS and Spatialite.
 .
 This package provides PHP bindings for SFCGAL: SFCGALGeometry plus the
 typed hierarchy (SFCGALPoint / SFCGALLineString / SFCGALPolygon /
 SFCGALSolid / ...), SFCGALPreparedGeometry and SFCGALException — for
 the 3D operations that GEOS does not provide (3D distance, intersection,
 union, difference, volume, tesselation, extrusion, straight skeleton,
 alpha shapes, alpha-wrapping 3D, Minkowski sums, 3D buffers, ...).
 .
 Companion to the php-geos package; bridges to/from GEOSGeometry via
 WKB round-trip.
